{
  "texts": [
    "Third, in this study, the positive attitude towards technology as well as the social influence were found as major factors driving the adoption of ChatGPT among the university students.",
    "A majority of the sample scored high on the \"attitude towards technology/social influence\" construct.",
    "The responses from participants in this study emphasized the key role of readiness to accept novel technological tools in achieving academic success.",
    "This result is conceivable considering that the inclination to embrace novel technological tools, as well as the influence of peers, collectively emerge as key determinants contributing to a successful adoption of new technologies within an educational context [93] [94] [95].",
    "Fourth, among the other factors identified as important determinants for ChatGPT adoption among university students in this study were the behavioral/cognitive factors."
  ]
}